{"tid":1158958,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逃犯條例未通過,港共政府就已經打壓民主派人士,簡直天理不容!","createTime":"2019-05-17T10:34:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T10:35:44.000Z","uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a2c3cc7f4236df8da8bf09b05edeca94d4bad7cc","tid":1158958,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190517/bkn-20190517174411117-0517_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190517%2Fbkn-20190517174411117-0517_00822_001.html&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEX6jPH3pfKCXBWMLigY0rPLs%3D&h=b76d4f67\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190517/bkn-20190517174411117-0517_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n警方拘捕<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民主派人士龍緯汶</span></span></strong>，懷疑他藉支援南亞人士期間，涉嫌非禮及製作兒童色情物品。他現正被扣留調查。網上近日流傳龍緯汶與南亞兒童的親暱照片，包括擁抱女童、讓女童坐大髀及與女童挨著睡覺。據了解，他拍攝一名年約7至8歲的女童私處。<br />\n<br />\n警方電子報案中心本周三(15日)接獲報案，指一名男子涉嫌於不同場合向一名兒童作出不必要的親密行為。西九龍總區刑事總部重案組人員接手調查案件，經深入調查後，今日(17日)上午約8時在荃灣區拘捕一名44歲姓龍本地男子，涉嫌非禮及製作兒童色情物品。他現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，被捕姓龍男子為民主派人士龍緯汶，為香港深水埗區議會社區事務委員會關注南亞裔人士生活工作小組成員及香港社區發展網絡總幹事，亦是香港作曲家及作詞家協會會員。"},{"pid":"a3aefe1e97aa40397aa00e46464c81bb5e828e08","tid":1158958,"uid":244332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T10:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}